<div class="article-cta-box">
  <h3>Need Cleaning or Landscaping in Charlottesville?</h3>
  <p>Dani Cleans serves Charlottesville, Albemarle County, and surrounding areas. Get a free, no-obligation estimate today.</p>
  <div class="article-cta-buttons">
    <a href="/pages/request-a-quote" class="article-cta-btn primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    <a href="tel:4343510335" class="article-cta-btn secondary">Call 434-351-0335</a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.article-cta-box {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a2a, #2d6a4f);
  color: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; text-align: center;
  margin: 40px 0;
}
.article-cta-box h3 { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.article-cta-box p { font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.article-cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.article-cta-btn {
  padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.article-cta-btn.primary { background: #fff; color: #2d6a4f; }
.article-cta-btn.secondary { border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); color: #fff; }
</style>
